<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif">
  <h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:16px">About StyleHub Miami</h1>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px">StyleHub Miami is your one-stop destination for discovering the best deals across multiple trusted retailers. We bring together millions of products from Amazon, AliExpress, Sephora, SHEIN, and Macy's — all in one place with secure checkout and tracked shipping.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:12px">How It Works</h2>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px">Browse and search across 5 major retailers simultaneously. When you find something you love, add it to your cart and check out securely through our platform. We handle the order routing, tracking, and customer support so you can shop with confidence.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:12px">Why Shop With Us</h2>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-bottom:32px">
    <div style="padding:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px">
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">Best Prices</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6">Compare prices across 5 stores to find the best deal. Save up to 70% on your favorite products.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px">
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">Secure Checkout</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6">SSL-encrypted checkout powered by Shopify. Your payment information is always protected.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px">
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">Tracked Shipping</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6">Every order comes with tracking. Know exactly where your package is at all times.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding:20px;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px">
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:8px">24/7 Support</h3>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6">Our team is always here to help. Contact us anytime with questions about your order.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;margin-bottom:12px">Our Trusted Partners</h2>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px">We source products from 5 verified retailers:</p>
  <ul style="font-size:14px;color:#555;line-height:2;padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:32px">
    <li>Amazon — World's largest online marketplace</li>
    <li>AliExpress — Global deals on millions of products</li>
    <li>Sephora — Premium beauty and skincare</li>
    <li>SHEIN — Trending fashion at unbeatable prices</li>
    <li>Macy's — Quality brands for home, fashion, and more</li>
  </ul>

  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:1.8">Based in Miami, FL. Questions? <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#e53e3e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Contact us</a>.</p>
</div>

